Synopsis is: Is our hero truly all good? Do you think he could resist the allure of cheating to win? His friends certainly are not a good influence in that regard. Either way the battle for getting I.A. day off begins. And what of Tay? Is she merely a victim of Vince's ambitions, or is he leading a righteous crusade against her for her crimes?
